[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0887","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0887.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1033","title":"Microsoft Outlook Express POP3 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Outlook Express 4.72.3612.1700 之前版本存在 POP3 协议处理缺陷，远程攻击者可通过发送包含特殊构造的 \"..\" 字符串的恶意邮件，诱使 Outlook 重新进入 POP3 命令模式，导致 POP3 会话挂起无法继续处理后续邮件，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Outlook Express 4.27.3110 及 4.72.3120 等版本，攻击者无需认证即可触发，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1033"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:33.953","remediation":"将 Microsoft Outlook Express 升级至 4.72.3612.1700 或更高版本，此版本修复了包含 \"..\" 序列的恶意邮件导致 POP3 命令模式循环挂起的问题。如无法升级，建议禁用 POP3 邮箱功能或改用 IMAP 协议收信作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92647407427342&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92663402004275&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/252","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19207","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1033.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1033.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1033","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1033.json","https://github.com/xaitax/SploitScan/blob/e7c7a6140bbd6a60ea622b6124620fbed9d12332/README.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1033.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1033.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-935q-jf44-fq38/GHSA-935q-jf44-fq38.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0887.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0608","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0608.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0754","title":"ISC INN inndstart 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"INN（InterNetNews）新闻服务器中的 inndstart 程序存在权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过设置 INNCONF 环境变量指定恶意配置文件，从而以提升后的权限执行任意操作。该漏洞影响早期版本的 INN 新闻服务器软件，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，利用方式简单，可导致系统完全受控。建议升级至最新版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0754"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:59.240","remediation":"升级 INN 至 2.2 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。无法升级时，移除 inndstart 的 SUID 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/inndstart），或限制用户对 INNCONF 环境变量的设置权限，避免低权限用户通过该变量加载恶意配置文件提升权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.redhat.com/corp/support/errata/inn99_05_22.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/255"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0608.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0501","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0501.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0773","title":"Sun Solaris 7.0 lpset 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 7.0 的 /usr/bin/lpset 程序中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地低权限用户可通过向该程序提交特制的参数或环境变量触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖内存空间，从而获取 root 权限，完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 7.0 版本，攻击者需具有本地登录权限，无需网络访问即可完成提权利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0773"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.700","remediation":"安装 Sun 官方补丁 106980（Solaris 7 适用），或升级至 Solaris 8 及以上版本。临时缓解措施：以 root 执行 `chmod 555 /usr/bin/lpset` 移除 setuid 位，限制本地普通用户以提权方式运行该程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.netspace.org/cgi-bin/wa?A2=ind9905B&L=bugtraq&P=R2017","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19206"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0501.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0568","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0568.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0806","title":"Sun Solaris dtprintinfo 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 7.0 系统中的 dtprintinfo 工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，该程序位于 /usr/dt/bin/dtprintinfo，在处理特制输入时未正确验证缓冲区边界，导致可被利用覆盖内存数据。本地攻击者可通过向 dtprintinfo 传递超长参数触发溢出，进而以 root 权限执行任意代码，实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 Solaris 7.0 版本，需本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0806"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.767","remediation":"安装 Sun 官方补丁 107080-01（SPARC 平台）或 107081-01（x86 平台）修复 dtprintinfo 缓冲区溢出漏洞。若无法打补丁，立即移除 dtprintinfo 的 setuid 位：chmod -s /usr/dt/bin/dtprintinfo，或限制仅管理员可执行：chmod 700 /usr/dt/bin/dtprintinfo。如不需要 CDE 打印功能可直接删除该二进制文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6552","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19205"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0568.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0568.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0568.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0356","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0356.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0738","title":"Microsoft Internet Information Server code.asp 示例文件任意文件读取漏洞","description":"IIS 和 Site Server 中自带的 code.asp 示例文件存在任意文件读取漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用该示例文件读取服务器上的任意文件内容，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Microsoft IIS 及 Site Server 的多个版本，攻击条件低，无需身份认证即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0738"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.270","remediation":"立即删除 IIS 及 Site Server 中 code.asp、showcode.asp、viewcode.asp 等示例文件查看器（默认不安装于 IIS，但在 Site Server 中默认安装），或安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-013 提供的补丁。作为临时缓解措施，可通过 NTFS ACL 严格限制这些文件的读取权限，并将示例文件移出 Web 内容目录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-013"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0356.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0355","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0355.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0737","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 showcode.asp 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 中的 showcode.asp 示例脚本存在任意文件读取漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过构造特制的 HTTP 请求查看服务器上的任意文件内容，导致系统配置文件、源代码等敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 IIS 4.0 及 Site Server 相关版本，利用方式简单，危害等级中等，Microsoft 已在后续更新中建议删除该示例脚本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0737"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.140","remediation":"删除 IIS 安装目录下的 `\\IIS Samples\\Scripts` 目录及其所有文件，特别是 `showcode.asp` 和 `viewcode.asp` 等示例脚本。对于生产环境，不应部署任何 IIS 示例文件。同时确认 IIS 虚拟目录中未映射非必要的脚本映射（如 `.htr`、`.idc` 等）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-013"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0355.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0352","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0352.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0736","title":"Microsoft IIS showcode.asp 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"IIS 和 Site Server 中默认安装的 showcode.asp 示例文件存在任意文件读取漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可利用该漏洞读取服务器上的任意文件，包括系统配置文件、源代码等敏感信息。该漏洞影响 Microsoft IIS 4.0 及 Site Server 3.0 版本，属于信息泄露类安全风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0736"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.020","remediation":"删除 IIS 安装目录下的 `showcode.asp` 示例文件（通常位于 `\\InetPub\\wwwroot\\Samples\\`），或移除整个 Samples 虚拟目录。升级至 IIS 5.0 及以上版本以彻底消除该旧版示例文件带来的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-013","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A932","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19129"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0352.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0245","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0245.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0686","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server HP-UX 平台长 URL 请求拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server（NES）在 HP-UX 平台的 HP Virtual Vault（VVOS）环境中存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制超长 URL 请求，触发服务进程崩溃或资源耗尽，导致服务器无法正常处理合法用户请求。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，攻击门槛较低，主要影响 HP Virtual Vault 操作系统上运行的 NES Web 服务，在特定网络条件下可造成拒绝服务。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0686"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.783","remediation":"建议立即升级 Netscape Enterprise Server 至 3.6 SP2 及以上版本（HP-UX 对应安全补丁编号 PHSS_20316）。在反向代理或负载均衡器（如 HP-UX Apache-based Web Server）上限制 URL 长度不超过 4096 字节，拒绝超过阈值的请求。配置 WAF 规则过滤包含超长路径的 HTTP 请求。由于 NES 及 HP-UX Virtual Vault 均已停止技术支持，长期解决方案应迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server）和操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-046.shtml","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9906-098","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0686.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0686","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0686.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0686.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mrj2-v329-4cm9/GHSA-mrj2-v329-4cm9.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0686.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0245.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0245.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1808","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1808.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1241","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer ActiveX FileSystemObject 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 浏览器在安全级别设置为\"中\"以下时存在任意命令执行漏洞。远程攻击者可构造恶意网页，利用 FileSystemObject ActiveX 控件绕过安全机制，当用户使用受影响的 IE 浏览器访问该恶意页面时，攻击者可在目标系统上以当前用户权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响早期版本的 Internet Explorer 浏览器。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1241"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:01.150","remediation":"将 Internet Explorer 安全区域设置为\"中\"或更高等级以阻止低权限 ActiveX 控件执行；在注册表 HKLM\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\ActiveX Compatibility\\{0D43FE01-F093-11CF-8940-00A0C9054228} 下创建 DWORD 值 Compatibility Flags 为 0x400（Kill Bit）以禁用 FileSystemObject 控件；安装 Microsoft 针对该漏洞发布的最新 IE 安全累积更新。由于 Internet Explorer 已停止技术支持，强烈建议升级至 Microsoft Edge 等现代浏览器以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://oliver.efri.hr/~crv/security/bugs/NT/activex4.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2173","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-1241.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1241.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1241","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1241.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1241.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qxqf-rx8x-jgrw/GHSA-qxqf-rx8x-jgrw.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1241.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87843/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000628.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1808.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0925","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0925.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1079","title":"IBM AIX 4.3 ptrace 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 4.3 操作系统的 ptrace 系统调用存在权限验证缺陷，本地攻击者可利用 ptrace 附加到一个 setgid 权限的进程，从而继承该进程的提权权限，导致本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.3 版本，攻击者需拥有本地账户，无需其他特殊条件即可利用，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1079"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.653","remediation":"升级至 AIX 5.1 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本修复。IBM 已针对此问题发布 APAR IX84149，建议安装对应补丁。如无法升级，可通过限制 ptrace 系统调用的用户权限（仅允许 root 用户使用）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92601792420088&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93587956513233&w=2","http://www-1.ibm.com/servlet/support/manager?rs=0&rt=0&org=apars&doc=08E0B1A1B85472A1852567C90031BB36","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/439","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1079.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1079.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1079","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1079.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1079.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1079.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qpvh-wpmg-5vw6/GHSA-qpvh-wpmg-5vw6.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--64058aab-083d-4dce-afe1-93ac7b4f3bdb.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000627.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0925.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1005","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1005.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1195","title":"NAI VirusScan NT 升级验证缺陷漏洞","description":"NAI VirusScan NT 4.0.2 在进行 FTP 在线更新病毒定义文件 scan.dat 时，由于未正确验证文件是否完整写入磁盘，即在更新流程完成后返回成功状态，导致即使病毒库文件实际未被正确修改，软件仍向管理员报告更新成功。攻击者可通过中间人攻击或控制更新服务器向目标推送无效或过时的病毒定义，使系统长期处于未受保护状态，严重影响主机安全性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1195"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:55.253","remediation":"升级至 Network Associates VirusScan NT 4.0.3a 或更高版本。如无法升级，可临时关闭 VirusScan 引擎后等待数秒使系统释放 scan.dat 文件句柄，再手动将最新病毒定义文件复制到 VirusScan NT 安装目录覆盖旧文件。完成操作后应通过反病毒控制台检查「Created On」日期是否已更新，以确认定义文件确实被正确替换。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92588169005196&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92587579032534&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/169","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1195.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1195","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1195.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1195.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5783344e7c4adc3f449b78e346f760d75b095a9c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pm4g-gv9m-qf7v/GHSA-pm4g-gv9m-qf7v.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/169/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1195.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/151244184a2592693ea242321c22fa26af96c58c/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1005.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0938","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0938.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1097","title":"Microsoft NetMeeting 剪贴板信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft NetMeeting 2.1 存在剪贴板信息泄露漏洞。当聊天框为空时，攻击者可通过在聊天框中发送 CTRL-C 快捷键操作，触发对另一客户端剪贴板内容的读取，导致用户剪贴板中的敏感信息（如密码、文本内容）被未授权获取。该漏洞影响 NetMeeting 2.1 版本，攻击者需与目标处于同一会话中方可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1097"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:42.933","remediation":"建议立即卸载或禁用 Microsoft NetMeeting 2.1（通过控制面板 → 添加/删除程序 → 删除 NetMeeting 组件；Windows 98 可在安装光盘中删除通讯组件），避免在会议中使用聊天功能时泄露剪贴板内容。对于仍依赖远程协作功能的用户，应迁移至受支持的替代方案（如 Microsoft Teams、Skype for Business）或使用 PGP 加密剪贴板内容作为临时缓解措施。后续的 Windows 版本已移除 NetMeeting，不再受此漏洞影响。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92586457816446&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2187","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1097.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1097","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1097.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1097.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1097.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mqf5-wgx4-qfwq/GHSA-mqf5-wgx4-qfwq.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88089/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1097.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000625.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0938.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0861","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0861.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1012","title":"Lotus Domino SMTP 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Lotus Domino 4.6.1 的 SMTP 组件在处理超长字符串时存在未正确边界检查的漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器的 SMTP 端口发送特制超长字符串，触发缓冲区溢出或异常处理错误，导致邮件服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 AS/400 平台的 Lotus Domino 4.6.1 版本并可能波及其他操作系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1012"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.237","remediation":"升级 Lotus Domino 至 4.6.2 或更高版本，该版本在 SMTP 服务中增加了输入长度校验，防止超长字符串导致缓冲区崩溃。如使用更现代的版本，建议迁移至 HCL Domino 12.x 或 14.x 长期支持版。同时可在 SMTP 网关或防火墙层面配置最大行长度限制（如 RFC 2821 建议的 998 字符），作为额外深度防御措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13527","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/173","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1012","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-10xx/CVE-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/dcc6735c9c3e50e93de820fa1ac9c54ecf6b2577/1999/CVE-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1012.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1012.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0861.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0570","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0570.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0807","title":"Netscape Directory Server 安装过程敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"Netscape Directory Server 在安装过程中存在敏感信息泄露漏洞。安装程序将管理员密码、配置凭证等敏感数据以明文方式保存在本地文件中，且未设置充分的访问权限控制。本地攻击者可通过读取这些文件获取敏感信息，进而可能提升权限或获取目录服务器的管理访问权限。该漏洞影响早期版本的 Netscape Directory Server，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0807"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.883","remediation":"由于 Netscape Directory Server 已停止维护，建议迁移至 389 Directory Server、Red Hat Directory Server 或 OpenLDAP 等现代替代品。迁移前应立即检查并收紧安装目录文件权限（如 /usr/netscape/server4/ 等），移除 world-readable 权限并清理安装过程中遗留的 .inf/.log/响应文件等含明文凭据的临时文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0807"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0570.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0481","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0481.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0764","title":"NetBSD NetBSD ARP 静态条目覆盖漏洞","description":"NetBSD 系统 ARP 协议实现存在安全缺陷，远程攻击者可向目标网络发送伪造的 ARP 数据包，覆盖系统本应受保护的静态 ARP 缓存条目。攻击者利用此漏洞可实施中间人攻击或拒绝服务攻击，劫持或阻断目标主机与网络中其他设备的正常通信。该漏洞影响 NetBSD 系统，CVSS 评分 6.4。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0764"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.597","remediation":"立即升级 NetBSD 至 1.4.1 或更高版本（1999 年 5 月已发布修复补丁），该版本内核已禁止 ARP 包覆盖静态 ARP 条目。如无法升级，可通过 `arp -s` 配合 `-f` 参数将静态 ARP 条目写入 `/etc/ethers` 并设置只读权限，同时在交换机上配置端口安全 (port security) 和动态 ARP 检测 (DAI) 以限制 ARP 欺骗攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6539"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0481.toml"}]